title: QI XL Series 12 L - GHOST DOG
description:
The twelfth series of QI, the BBC comedy panel game television show hosted by Stephen Fry, started on 3 October 2014. As each series of QI is based around a letter of the alphabet, all episodes in the series had themes beginning with the letter "L".
As with some previous series, an ongoing theme in the series was the "Spend a Penny" card. Each episode featured one question to which the answer was "lavatorial", and the panelist who identified the question by raising the Penny-shaped joker won bonus points.
Guests making their first appearance in this series are Aisling Bea, Carrie Fisher, Tony Hawks, Adam Hills, Lloyd Langford, Kathy Lette, Claudia O'Doherty, Lucy Porter and Suggs.

Episodes:

1. L-Animals
2. Location, Location, Location
3. Language & Literature
4. Levity
5. Lenses
6. Liblabble
7. Lethal
8. Lovely
9. Ladies and Gents
10. Lying
11. Lumped Together
12. No L (Christmas Special)
13. Lucky Losers
14. Little and Large
15. Long Lost
16. Landmarks
